<BaseLayout title="Venue">
  <main class="mx-8 md:mx-16">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl mb-8">Venue</h1>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Location: Levi, Lapland</h3>
        <p>
          During the congress, participants can choose from a range of
          accommodation options to suit different needs and budgets, all
          conveniently located near the Levi Mountain Centre. The congress will
          take place at the Levi Mountain Centre in Hotel Hullu Poro, which
          offers quality accommodations and easy access to all events. A quota
          of rooms has been reserved for participants, along with various
          options including hotels and cabins, allowing attendees to select the
          most suitable option for their stay.
        </p>
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1506.9934144192425!2d24.80723607790104!3d67.8081066559591!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x45d24d5a87b3f0fd%3A0xd00dac320805b483!2sHullu%20Poro%20(Hotel%20Crazy%20Reindeer)!5e0!3m2!1sde!2sch!4v1727347059773!5m2!1sde!2sch"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          class="w-full max-md:h-[300px] md:h-[500px]"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="max-md:mt-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl mb-8">Travel</h1>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Flight to Kittil√§</li>
          <li>Bus/taxi to Levi (20min)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
